AAP, BJP, and Congress promise welfare schemes while targeting the significant Poorvanchali vote share. Rigorous security with 60,000 personnel ensures a fair poll at 13,766 booths. Voting runs 7 AM to 6 PM, with counting set post-poll closure.
title: Delhi hits the button today, stage set for a thrilling 3-way contest
